                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "明珠甲胄"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超载</span>：本伤害<span>+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">超导</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">原激化</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成使下3次草/雷伤害+1的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">激化领域</span><span>]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/17/157749474/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_1703239395055626056.png",
